SUB_W12_FUNC_BOFO_MATCHES_200_CUT_000_04.text:
Our only lead is the final emperor's palace;
the triangle's gotta be connected to that
place someway, somehow.

SUB_W12_EVAR_BOFO_ICECASTLE_110_CUT_000_.text:
We never should've brought you here, kid;
this whole thing is one giant trap.
Better just let us handle this.

SUB_W12_EVAR_BOFO_ICECASTLE_210_CUT_000_.text:
There is nothing for you here, travelers;
your mission lies elsewhere. There is no
cause for you to wager your life upon this.
